{
  "table": "story_event_announce_detail",
  "row_count": 129,
  "columns": [
    "id",
    "announce_id",
    "order",
    "cue_name",
    "text_message"
  ],
  "rows": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "announce_id": 1,
      "order": 1,
      "cue_name": "snd_voi_event_090004_0100",
      "text_message": "That bride just now was so beautiful!"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "announce_id": 1,
      "order": 2,
      "cue_name": "snd_voi_event_090004_0101",
      "text_message": "Aw, I'm jealous! I wanna wear a dress like that!"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "announce_id": 1,
      "order": 3,
      "cue_name": "snd_voi_event_090004_0102",
      "text_message": "A wedding dress, huh? The elegant design is rather captivating..."
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "announce_id": 1,
      "order": 4,
      "cue_name": "snd_voi_event_090004_0103",
      "text_message": "Riiight? ♪ You would look so good in one, Air Groove!"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "announce_id": 1,
      "order": 5,
      "cue_name": "snd_voi_event_090004_0104",
      "text_message": "What do you say to bewitching everyone?"
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "announce_id": 1,
      "order": 6,
      "cue_name": "snd_voi_event_090004_0105",
      "text_message": "What kind of outfit are you planning on making me wear?"
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "announce_id": 1,
      "order": 7,
      "cue_name": "snd_voi_event_090004_0106",
      "text_message": "I'm sure there are others who would look good in a wedding dress too. For example, hm... how about Dober?"
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "announce_id": 1,
      "order": 8,
      "cue_name": "snd_voi_event_090004_0107",
      "text_message": "Yeah, true! But you know, I bet everyone would look good in one! ♪ There are so many different kinds of wedding dresses, after all!"
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "announce_id": 1,
      "order": 9,
      "cue_name": "snd_voi_event_090004_0108",
      "text_message": "Some look fit for a princess, and some are biiiig and poofy. ♪ I wonder who from the academy they'd suit?"
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "announce_id": 1,
      "order": 10,
      "cue_name": "snd_voi_event_090004_0109",
      "text_message": "...Stop letting your weird imagination run wild."
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "announce_id": 1,
      "order": 11,
      "cue_name": "snd_voi_event_090004_0110",
      "text_message": "Stay tuned for Umamusume: Pretty Derby's newest story event—Racing Hearts Beauty in Bloom."
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "announce_id": 1,
      "order": 12,
      "cue_name": "snd_voi_event_090004_0111",
      "text_message": "Take off in a twinkly dress. ☆"
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "announce_id": 2,
      "order": 1,
      "cue_name": "snd_voi_event_090002_0100",
      "text_message": "Check out the world's strongest racer! I'm peak! I'm power! I'm El—star of the Umamusume world!"
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "announce_id": 2,
      "order": 2,
      "cue_name": "snd_voi_event_090002_0101",
      "text_message": "You appear to be in good spirits, El. But being the star of one world doesn't necessarily mean you'd excel in others."
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "announce_id": 2,
      "order": 3,
      "cue_name": "snd_voi_event_090002_0102",
      "text_message": "Qué?! Other what? Are you sayin' there are other <i>worlds</i> out there?!"
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "announce_id": 2,
      "order": 4,
      "cue_name": "snd_voi_event_090002_0103",
      "text_message": "No, not quite. I've heard that Tracen Academy has new machines that let you experience games in virtual reality."
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "announce_id": 2,
      "order": 5,
      "cue_name": "snd_voi_event_090002_0104",
      "text_message": "For example... you could enter a kingdom of swords and sorcery."
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "announce_id": 2,
      "order": 6,
      "cue_name": "snd_voi_event_090002_0105",
      "text_message": "Imagine exploring a fantasy world, with your own Umamusume body and abilities..."
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "announce_id": 2,
      "order": 7,
      "cue_name": "snd_voi_event_090002_0106",
      "text_message": "Oooooh! Kinda like an Umamusume isekai!"
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "announce_id": 2,
      "order": 8,
      "cue_name": "snd_voi_event_090002_0107",
      "text_message": "If I got isekai'd into a game world, I'd definitely be the Eternal Champion— the hero of the El-ell Saga!"
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "announce_id": 2,
      "order": 9,
      "cue_name": "snd_voi_event_090002_0108",
      "text_message": "C'mon Grass, we've gotta go check it out! It'll be like a mini vacation, and we can brawl our way to video game glory!"
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "announce_id": 2,
      "order": 10,
      "cue_name": "snd_voi_event_090002_0109",
      "text_message": "Oh, fine. I guess I'll have to go with you. I'd be too worried letting you go all on your own."
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "announce_id": 2,
      "order": 11,
      "cue_name": "snd_voi_event_090002_0110",
      "text_message": "Next time on Umamusume: Pretty Derby—\"Uma Quest: Epic Odyssey\"!"
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "announce_id": 2,
      "order": 12,
      "cue_name": "snd_voi_event_090002_0111",
      "text_message": "Stay tuned for El's Condor punches and my healing magic! ♪"
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "announce_id": 3,
      "order": 1,
      "cue_name": "snd_voi_event_090005_0100",
      "text_message": "Hmm. There are so many different kinds of swimsuits nowadays."
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "announce_id": 3,
      "order": 2,
      "cue_name": "snd_voi_event_090005_0101",
      "text_message": "No kidding! That orange one is so cute."
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "announce_id": 3,
      "order": 3,
      "cue_name": "snd_voi_event_090005_0102",
      "text_message": "They have everything from sporty ones to the classic two-piece designs."
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "announce_id": 3,
      "order": 4,
      "cue_name": "snd_voi_event_090005_0103",
      "text_message": "Ah, I love that one with the ribbons..."
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "announce_id": 3,
      "order": 5,
      "cue_name": "snd_voi_event_090005_0104",
      "text_message": "That one's nice! I bet you would look great in it!"
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "announce_id": 3,
      "order": 6,
      "cue_name": "snd_voi_event_090005_0105",
      "text_message": "You know, I think I saw someone picking out a new swimsuit from a magazine the other day..."
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "announce_id": 3,
      "order": 7,
      "cue_name": "snd_voi_event_090005_0106",
      "text_message": "I guess it's already swimsuit season, huh?"
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "announce_id": 3,
      "order": 8,
      "cue_name": "snd_voi_event_090005_0107",
      "text_message": "So it is. Come to think of it, I don't have anything fun planned for the summer."
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "announce_id": 3,
      "order": 9,
      "cue_name": "snd_voi_event_090005_0108",
      "text_message": "Haha. Me neither. My training schedule is too packed for anything like that..."
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "announce_id": 3,
      "order": 10,
      "cue_name": "snd_voi_event_090005_0109",
      "text_message": "Next time on Umamusume: Pretty Derby—Beaches, Bathing Suits & Blazing Trails."
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "announce_id": 3,
      "order": 11,
      "cue_name": "snd_voi_event_090005_0110",
      "text_message": "There'll be swimsuits, pools, and disco fever! ...Wait, disco fever?"
    },
